subject: Horse Racing
Jockeys, Drivers and Trainers
lead_paragraph: Game On Dude carried Chantel Sutherland to victory in the $500,000 Hollywood Gold Cup in Inglewood, Calif., making her the first female jockey to win the 73-year-old race.
